snippet: Federer stopped the top-seeded Djokovic’s ATP World Tour Finals winning streak at 15, winning in London to reach the semifinals.
abstract: Roger Federer beats Novak Djokovic to reach semifinals at ATP World Tour Finals in London; other tennis news noted.
lead_paragraph: Federer stopped the top-seeded Djokovic’s ATP World Tour Finals winning streak at 15, winning in London to reach the semifinals.

headline.main: Roger Federer Ends Novak Djokovic’s Streak
